air and expansion work.  This initiative aims to provide dignified housing for economically weaker families.  The project budget has significantly increased under the current administration.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/delhi-government-accelerates-allotment-of-7400-ews-flats-at-bhalswa/132455560?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-2071122/132455560.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}